$OpenBSD: patch-girepository_giroffsets_c,v 1.6 2011/06/15 09:46:40 jasper Exp $

Prevent redefinition of ALIGN in giroffsets.c with /usr/include/machine/param.h

https://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=652625

--- girepository/giroffsets.c.orig	Wed Nov 17 15:02:51 2010
